ZH: 我买了几个梨。
EN: I bought a few pears.

ZH: 梨是个很多人喜欢吃的水果。
EN: Pears are a fruit that many people enjoy eating.

ZH: 妈妈用梨做了一个梨塔。
EN: Mom made a pear tart.

ZH: 我喜欢吃生的梨。
EN: I like to eat pears raw.

ZH: 他在超市买了一箱梨。
EN: He bought a box of pears at the supermarket.

ZH: 梨汁是一种很受欢迎的饮料。
EN: Pear juice is a popular beverage.

ZH: 梨树上挂满了成熟的梨。
EN: The pear tree is full of ripe pears.

ZH: 我的早餐里放了一些梨片。
EN: I put some slices of pear in my breakfast.

ZH: 你知道梨有很多不同的品种吗？
EN: Do you know that there are many different varieties of pears?

ZH: 小孩子们都很喜欢吃梨。
EN: Kids all love to eat pears.

ZH: 我家后院有棵梨树。
EN: There is a pear tree in my backyard.

ZH: 梨皮富含纤维。
EN: Pear skin is rich in fiber.

ZH: 那个梨很甜。
EN: That pear is very sweet.

ZH: 梨树上的梨熟透了。
EN: The pears on the pear tree are ripe.

ZH: 梨是一种低热量的水果。
EN: Pears are a low-calorie fruit.

ZH: 那个熟透的梨看起来很好吃。
EN: That ripe pear looks delicious.

ZH: 我喜欢梨和奶酪一起吃。
EN: I like to eat pears with cheese.

ZH: 梨是人们常常送作为礼物的水果。
EN: Pears are a fruit that people often give as gifts.

ZH: 我家的梨树今年结了很多梨。
EN: My pear tree has produced a lot of pears this year.

ZH: 梨的营养价值很高。
EN: Pears have high nutritional value.
